# GTK Calculator - Jeremy Lawrence

## Description
A simple calculator in C created with GTK4 widget toolkit.

## Prerequisites
Ensure that the following are installed:
- GCC (or another C compiler)
- GTK4 libraries
- pkg-config

## Installation

### Option 1: Use Setup Script (Recommended for Linux/MacOS)
1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/jeremlaw/gtkalculator.git
   cd gtkalculator

2. Run the installation script:
    chmod +x install.sh
    ./install.sh

### Option 2: Manual Installation
Steps for manual installation can be found at:
https://www.gtk.org/docs/installations/

## Building and Running the Program
1. Once the dependencies are installed, build the program using `make`.
2. After building, run the program using `./calc`. 

